org.apache.taverna.t2referencetest

Class GreenReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.reference.AbstractExternalReference
      • org.apache.taverna.t2referencetest.GreenReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, ExternalReferenceSPI

    public class GreenReference
extends AbstractExternalReference
implements ExternalReferenceSPI
    GreenReferences carry their data as an internal String and have a resolution cost of 1.1f whatever the value of that string.
    Author:
    Tom Oinn

      • setContents

        public void setContents(String contents)
        Set the 'value' of this reference as a string. It's not really a reference type in any true sense of the word, but it'll do for testing the augmentation system. This method is really here so you can configure test beans from spring.
